begin model

############
# metadata #
############

#---
# References:
#  - Bar-Peled L, ..., Sabatini DM (2012) Cell 150: 1196-1208. [PMID: 22980980]
#  - Geiger T, ..., Mann M (2012) Mol Cell Proteomics 11: M111.014050 [PMID: 22278370]
#  - Gong R, ..., Xu Y (2011) Genes Dev 25: 1668-1673. [PMID: 21816923]
#  - Hein MY, ..., Mann M (2015) Cell 163: 712-723. [PMID: 26496610]
#  - Kulak NA, ..., Mann M (2014) Nat Methods 11: 319-324. [PMID: 24487582]
#  - Kurzbauer R, ..., Clausen T (2004) PNAS 101: 10984-10989. [PMID: 15263099]
#  - Levine TP, ..., Barr FA (2013) Small GTPases 4: 62-69. [PMID: 23511850]
#  - Lunin VV, ..., Sacher M (2004) J Biol Chem 279: 23422-23430. [PMID: 15016825]
#  - Miertzschke M, ..., Wittinghofer A (2011). EMBO J 30: 4185-4197. [PMID: 21847100]
#  - Powis K, ..., Ding j (2015) Cell Res 25: 1043-1059. [PMID: 26206314]
#  - Sancak Y, ..., Sabatini DM (2010) Cell 141: 290-303. [PMID: 20381137]
#  - Sekiguchi T, ..., Nishimoto T (2001) J Biol Chem 276: 7246-7257. [PMID: 11073942]
#  - Tan CW, ..., Burgess AW (2012) PLoS ONE 7: e31882. [PMID: 22363759]
